/ Question Info ===============================================
/ Determining DNA Health
/
/ Given:
/ - A list of genes and associated health values
/ - A DNA string
/ - Multiple queries with index ranges [start, end]
/
/ Task:
/ - For each query:
/   * Only consider genes within index range
/   * Compute total health score based on occurrences in DNA
/
/ Return:
/ - Minimum and maximum health scores across all queries
/ =============================================================